Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貨物就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.31,0:03:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.13,0:03:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送貨的，辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.17,0:03:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作結束了，快回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把艾兒…放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.62,0:03:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是另一半酬勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.89,0:03:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是亞力克斯‧羅威嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去裝貨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.93,0:04:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛溫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.97,0:04:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別對貨物太粗魯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.77,0:04:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.55,0:04:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.16,0:05:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.15,0:05:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.09,0:05:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還趕得上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.91,0:05:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊\N你就算用填充劑作應急處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.71,0:05:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有燃料還是飛不起來的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃料我現在就去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.62,0:06:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢著慢著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難不成要用那傢伙的燃料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.50,0:06:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.94,0:06:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人已經…死了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.75,0:06:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，還是算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了艾兒\N總共已經死了三個人了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.99,0:06:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也看到\N亞力克斯他的眼神了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種人居然也能在天上飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.70,0:06:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他的眼神可不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好好看著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.55,0:07:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著，任務已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.32,0:07:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經把貨送到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任務就到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在沒問清楚\N他們打算怎麼處理艾兒之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務還不算結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.09,0:07:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貨物如果沒有安全送達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.36,0:07:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務就等於失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好幼稚哦，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.26,0:07:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…忘了把這帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們幫她送去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.70,0:07:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒她應該需要這個的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險度恐怕可以到十顆星呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.57,0:08:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇妳也滿幼稚的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪比得上克勞士你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.54,0:08:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這燃料是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.31,0:08:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濃度高得一塌糊塗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不調整混合比例的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.38,0:08:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這小傢伙的引擎會燒壞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底是何方神聖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然可以用這麼厲害的燃料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會是…基爾特公會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.93,0:08:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.73,0:08:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為就那樣丟掉\N未免太可惜了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.53,0:09:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說可以拿來維修先鋒艇呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了妳這個性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,存錢可是很重要的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.27,0:09:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面\N艾兒薇絲‧漢彌爾敦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.90,0:09:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫蘇菲亞\N是這艘船的副艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.71,0:09:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.34,0:09:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想必累了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.91,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保證妳可以在這裡\N過得很舒適的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼需要別客氣儘管說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以為妳做些什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.36,0:10:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒我會送吃的過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就好好休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.74,0:10:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要當個保姆\N恐怕妳的笑容還嫌不夠哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜妳在偷看嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.91,0:10:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會做那麼不識趣的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是直覺啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.45,0:10:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過真想不到副艦長\N妳居然會親自來照顧小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要換妳來做做看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.81,0:10:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜‧魏斯洛跟您報到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貨物呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛才醒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.81,0:10:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.95,0:11:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魏斯洛，妳到皇帝那裡跑一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他貨物已經安全送到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後桅桿觀測台傳來報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.93,0:11:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七點鐘方向有一架\N來路不明的先鋒艇正在接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.03,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃料不夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算純度再怎麼高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.45,0:11:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照你這種飆法\N頂多也只夠單程用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.79,0:11:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.92,0:11:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.19,0:11:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，給我逮到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.86,0:11:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱們上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.60,0:11:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是發光信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.13,0:11:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…它說不准靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.87,0:11:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用理它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…還是得回它一句話才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一句話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，好歹這也是工作嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禮貌上應該要打聲招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.96,0:12:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦要對我們開砲了\N妳究竟打了什麼招呼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.43,0:12:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只說了\N我們送東西過來而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.20,0:12:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被那種東西打中了\N保證一命嗚呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.90,0:12:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝上去，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要上了船\N他們就拿我們沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼真的開砲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.43,0:12:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要從後面繞過去，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.99,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.96,0:13:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見吧，我短暫的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.31,0:13:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的對空砲火是在玩假的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那架先鋒艇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魏斯洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它真像以前的妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這就和艾麗絲蒂亞\N一起出發到皇帝那邊去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天你還挺健談的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.88,0:14:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高度沒辦法拉高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.68,0:14:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃料也到了極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.05,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是墜落還是擊落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是死路一條啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，不可以放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.92,0:14:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我緊急迫降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.19,0:14:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確定先鋒艇已打開空氣煞車器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我居然還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的小羊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接…接得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把鉤子找個地方鉤起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.07,0:15:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，到這邊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有升降機\N說不定可以利用它到上面去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說他們為什麼要停止射擊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.09,0:15:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛明明就是\N擊落我們的好機會說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜他們根本就\N沒把我們看在眼裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這地方那麼大\N真的找得到艾兒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.80,0:15:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只希望他們\N不要突然朝我們開槍才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來像停機庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.61,0:15:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有人耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法再往上了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.89,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.03,0:16:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是曾經救過我們的那架先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.01,0:16:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.75,0:16:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來這裡幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.86,0:16:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不滿意剛才的另一半酬勞嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.49,0:16:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的強行登艦\N我還是頭一次看到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.67,0:16:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說不滿意我們也一樣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.87,0:16:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看銀之戰艦都被你們\N用那架破銅爛鐵給刮傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.71,0:16:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破銅爛鐵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.27,0:17:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於傷到銀之戰艦的人\N會有什麼下場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.75,0:17:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我來告訴你們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了任務而來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.12,0:17:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到這裡來\N總不會是為了送這布娃娃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是有人託我要交給艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是被你們帶到這裡來的\N那個小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.47,0:17:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,委託人就是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是送貨員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要完成了任務我立刻就回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.38,0:17:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我挺中意這小子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.12,0:17:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經在給他打分數啦\N蓋爾老爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.62,0:17:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你是不知道\N什麼叫有勇無謀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.69,0:17:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀，那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.93,0:17:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,東西就交給我吧，送貨員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.17,0:18:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,東西要直接交給本人\N這是規矩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.24,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是拜託人應該有的態度嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.41,0:18:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來不讓你吃點苦頭\N你是不會明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況不妙啊，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.02,0:18:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你最好別惹他們生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記得那傳聞嗎，肯定是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.76,0:18:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.79,0:18:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.73,0:18:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.83,0:18:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.00,0:18:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫我讓開耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.47,0:18:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你小子口氣挺跩的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.21,0:18:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像還沒弄清楚\N這裡是哪裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.51,0:18:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀呀，寇斯塔比下手還真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.28,0:18:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我來把垃圾給扔了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.92,0:18:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.06,0:18:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.99,0:18:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.93,0:18:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.96,0:19:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.00,0:19:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向隊長敬禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，你還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.65,0:19:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長在問你話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.85,0:19:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫克勞士‧沃卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.96,0:20:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會記住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,操作器檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.57,0:20:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儀表與計時器檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.64,0:20:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃料活栓保持開啟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混合劑充足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動前檢查項目全部完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.75,0:20:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.02,0:20:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們要找那個小孩\N可以到艦橋上問問看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳叫什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要人家報名字\N妳自己的就不說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你在跟誰說話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.37,0:20:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜‧魏斯洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會記住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.59,0:21:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魏斯洛隊長\N可是很少會問人家名字的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.96,0:21:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦橋一定就在這上面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.76,0:21:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.40,0:21:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.31,0:21:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不是走錯地方了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.74,0:21:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.28,0:22:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒她在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.25,0:22:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有東西要交給艾兒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.85,0:22:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.75,0:22:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士你振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.22,0:22:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.66,0:22:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.11,0:22:39.98,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.92,0:22:46.95,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く  でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.03,0:22:52.19,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.26,0:22:58.00,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.07,0:23:03.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你捨命奮鬥的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.84,0:23:12.65,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.72,0:23:18.55,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.62,0:23:24.36,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.43,0:23:30.10,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無論風有多麼強\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.17,0:23:36.04,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會折斷的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.11,0:23:45.28,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我會擁有那樣一對翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.46,0:23:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（下回預告）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.12,0:23:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒妳在這兒，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.66,0:23:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳問克勞士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.49,0:23:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士他就在妳面前啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.10,0:24:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，艾兒說你好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.90,0:24:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你那張腫得三倍大的臉\N可不可以處理一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.40,0:24:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳要我怎麼辦嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.21,0:24:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最後流亡 第六話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.95,0:24:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,審判者的攻擊\NArbiter attack
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.21,0:24:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.35,0:24:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦\N你是要我幫你說對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.48,0:24:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位觀眾，下週也敬請期待囉
